      <content type="html" xml:base="http://localhost:4000/lego-infinity-cube">&lt;p&gt;Instructions for building a LEGO infinity cube.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;There are a couple of videos on YouTube showing how to build the cube. Instructions are based on this one: &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=G3IW6K5JKHA&quot;&gt;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=G3IW6K5JKHA&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2 id=&quot;parts&quot;&gt;Parts&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Parts cost around 6 euros, when purchased through &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.lego.com/en-ie/pick-and-build/pick-a-brick&quot;&gt;LEGOâ€™s pick a brick&lt;/a&gt;.
List of parts, not taking the color into account.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;24 x &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.bricklink.com/v2/catalog/catalogitem.page?P=3023#T=C&quot;&gt;Plate 1x2 (3023)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;8 x &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.bricklink.com/v2/catalog/catalogitem.page?P=2429c01&quot;&gt;Hinge Plate 1x4 (6458397)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;8 x &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.bricklink.com/v2/catalog/catalogitem.page?P=99207&quot;&gt;Inverted Bracket 1x2-2x2 (99207)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;8 x &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.bricklink.com/v2/catalog/catalogitem.page?P=3068&quot;&gt;Tile 2x2 (3068)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;8 x &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.bricklink.com/v2/catalog/catalogitem.page?P=3069&quot;&gt;Tile 1x2 (3069)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

